      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-variable differential. The chassis has been properly sorted with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent suspension refresh utilizing polyurethane bushings for improved turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanicals are in excellent health, including a proactive rod bearing replacement and a cooling system overhaul to ensure reliability at the 8,000 RPM redline.",
