      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 powered by the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is mechanically robust, featuring a crisp 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M-differential lock for precise torque vectoring. The suspension is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), maintaining excellent damping characteristics across all modes. Crucially, preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its 'good' status, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition, delivering a linear power curve and an unmatched induction note. A technically sound specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
